      "content": "that makes sense. i noticed you mentioned europe and north america specifically. to be more precise for our creative teams, can you get a bit more specific about the look and feel? like, when we're casting models for the campaign, are we looking for a certain ethnicity or skin tone to represent this 'heritage' and 'prestige' vibe? i want to make sure we aren't missing the mark on what a high-status person actually looks like in these markets.",
